features: Fully Stock Your Classroom: Keep your classroom or remote learning setup fully stocked with this set of 6 packs of A8 wired headphones in different colors. Each set is individually wrapped for easy distribution.

High-Quality & Durable: Made with thickened nylon cable and gold-plated jacks, these headphones can withstand up to 44 lbs of weight and maintain a stable connection after over 10,000 uses. Invest in a reliable and long-lasting tool for your student's education.

Comfortable & Adjustable: With soft, over-ear breathable protein leather ear pads and a thick padded headband, these headphones eliminate ear fatigue and provide maximum comfort for hours of use. The adjustable headband is perfect for kids and teens of different sizes.

Enhance Learning Experiences: Featuring a built-in microphone, AILIHEN A8 headphones are perfect for interactive learning and online discussions. They also help students focus and perform better during standardized testing.
Universal Compatibility: Equipped with a 3.5mm jack, these headphones are compatible with most devices including Chromebooks, laptops, computers, and other mobile devices.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Weighing only 7oz and made with high-quality plastic, our headphones are built to last and withstand the wear and tear of daily use. With a stretchable headband, providing a comfortable and secure fit for kids and teens of different sizes.

Stay connected during online classes and video chats with our headphones' built-in microphone, ensuring seamless and clear communication with classmates and family. With a standard 3.5mm jack, those headphones easily connect to a variety of devices such as tablets, laptops, Chromebooks, and more. It's the ultimate "plug and play" solution for kids on the go.

What is the quantity of headphones included in this set? This bulk pack comprises 6 headphones in total. Are these headphones compatible with various devices like Chromebooks, laptops, tablets? Absolutely! These headphones are designed with a standard 3.5mm jack, making them compatible with most modern devices. What age range is this headphone suitable for? It is recommended for students from 2nd grade of elementary school to university level, and also suitable for adults. Do these headphones have a microphone? Can they be used with a Chromebook for exams that involve verbal answers? Absolutely, these wired headphones have an in-line microphone and are suitable for recording, including on a Chromebook for tasks where students need to provide verbal responses. What should I do if the headphones get damaged? Rest assured, AILIHEN provides complete coverage for one year to ensure your peace of mind. This includes addressing any concerns related to manufacturing, delivery, or normal wear during the initial year after your purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great set of headphones at a great price!
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this set of 6 headphones to use in a camp I’m running this summer. It will be used by children, but the headphones fit me well also. They arrived nicely packaged and in great condition. The sound quality is excellent, considering the price. I’m actually happily surprised how good it is. The volume goes pretty loud, actually louder than I need. Each set of headphones has a button on the side and a built in microphone. They seem sturdy and able to withstand being used by children. I like the different colors on each headphone so each can be told apart from the others. The ear cushions are very comfortable too. I also like that they fold up for easy storage and travel. They connect via a 3.5 mm jack to most laptops or computers. Overall I’m happy with this purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great deal for six pair!
reviews.reviewText: My wife is a teacher and just loves these for her kids when they do listening exercises. They are color coded and each kid has their own pair. They seem very rugged and fold up nicely to store them in the children's activity area. The cord is perfect length and durable and nylon tangle free. Also, the adjust for most size heads nicely. The sound quality is better than Bluetooth as these are wired and don't lose any fidelity. They also don't suffer from wireless latency. Super good deal for a six pack!! Highly recommend for learning, teaching, etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Product is Decent Quality for a Good Price
reviews.reviewText: Comfortability:These headphones are fairly comfortable, though they don't quite feel like they got around the ear comfortably. I could see them being a bit uncomfortable by the end of the day.Ease of use:Very easy to use, simple plug into a jack. Bluetooth would likely be more expensive but more helpful, especially with latest phone designs breeding out the headphone jack.Sound Quality: Decent for what you're paying for. The left side tends to be louder and less balanced, leaving your left side a bit blasted.Overall:These headphones will get the job done and are a good price for a six pack. I do plan on using them through my household. I paid about $45 for the six pack, so I would say that $7.50/pair is a fair price for what you get.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfortable and foldable Headphones for school/office
reviews.reviewText: We used these headphones for school and work. They’re surprisingly comfortable for older kids and teenagers in addition to adults. The sound quality is nice for school videos and music. The mike works and the headphones are adjustable for most. Excellent choice for a family with multiple kids in school who want something durable and easy to pack in a backpack. The cord is durable and they should last the school year. Nice option to gift to friends/family or not be sad if they get lost or damaged during school or travel.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality, very good performance headsets
reviews.reviewText: The set came well packaged and fully intact after a quick delivery. All headsets are individually wrapped. They fold together nicely, so they are easy to transport.Headsets have been designed with kids and young adults in mind - they are easy to use all around. At the same time they are made of sturdy materials and should last a good amount of time. Each headset has a different color on the outside of the ear piece, so they are easy to assign to people. The wire is sturdy and the connections are all re-enforced (see pictures).The headset is comfortable to wear, also for a long period of time. Microphone works great and picks up voice clearly. I tested this on various computers and handheld devices.Overall this set is a great value considering the quality of workmanship and price.
